{"tid":1687030,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點同bipolar disorder患者相處？","createTime":"2019-11-01T14:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T02:39:31.000Z","uid":311164,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8cca82b9782fd4a8f387c9a294ef68afc21bba60","tid":1687030,"uid":311164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:12:17.000Z","msg":"老母有躁鬱症<br />\n真心唔識相處<br />\n好多時候已經努力就佢安撫佢但有時真係頂唔順佢發佢脾氣<br />\n佢成日都有啲好無理嘅要求，就係要全世界跟佢做，唔聽佢講就發脾氣<br />\n我承認我同其他屋企人都做得唔夠好甚至好差，已經先入為主咗咩事都覺得係老母冇嘢揾嘢嚟搞，我都成日覺得自已好衰格對佢唔夠好，但又真係頂唔順<br />\n咁真係好惡頂呀嘛<br />\n唔想頂<br />\n一邊覺得自己好衰格知而不行好差，一邊覺得憑咩係佢大哂點解得我地要照顧佢感受<br />\n點算好<br />\n好驚佢自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點算好"},{"pid":"28418bafe4277d82c92866c9ed8541223dcd1d6b","tid":1687030,"uid":311164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:13:00.000Z","msg":"其實我同我老豆都真係好衰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4399f6887f0821b8df7625d7f49ac98fbf4bd28b","tid":1687030,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先40%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第二期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n民調眾籌LINK﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8N5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=bf9eb1cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"1498b818460c90c21d350e6a1aa261c9781ee78b","tid":1687030,"uid":311164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"但係我老母都好衰，我知佢有病控制唔到，但我都控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894151d455dcd6b32afd9d2d526ab1e85332d41a","tid":1687030,"uid":304249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:15:51.000Z","msg":"bipolar其實都一定要食藥<br />\n佢有冇準時按份量食呀？"},{"pid":"7489dd9bd49a23b120c402d39a8a11dcf5e11a95","tid":1687030,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"帶佢睇醫生，有藥物可幫助穩定情緒<br />\n另外樓主都要比多啲愛心包容你媽咪，<br />\n你媽咪唔係想搞事，可能係個病令佢控制唔到情緒，<br />\n先至有啲唔好既說話/行為<br />\n<br />\n你識得上網搵幫手已經好叻👍🏻 <br />\n希望你媽咪可以搵到個好醫生"},{"pid":"ab0302a1cbe85fc0c348939995f8194398fdbb04","tid":1687030,"uid":311164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"894151d455dcd6b32afd9d2d526ab1e85332d41a","tid":1687030,"uid":304249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:15:51.000Z","msg":"bipolar其實都一定要食藥<br />\n佢有冇準時按份量食呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"佢有呀，仲愈食愈多添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我好自責覺得自己衰仔。。。"},{"pid":"1ae517c4e10eff4bb0c51e1f2bbadb232fc87bd0","tid":1687030,"uid":311164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7489dd9bd49a23b120c402d39a8a11dcf5e11a95","tid":1687030,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"帶佢睇醫生，有藥物可幫助穩定情緒<br />\n另外樓主都要比多啲愛心包容你媽咪，<br />\n你媽咪唔係想搞事，可能係個病令佢控制唔到情緒，<br />\n先至有啲唔好既說話/行為<br />\n<br />\n你識得上網搵幫手已經好叻👍🏻 <br />\n希望你媽咪可以搵到個好醫生"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"佢係我出世前已經有病同睇開醫生，係呢幾年愈演愈烈，都頂咗好耐，嗰點係佢郁啲就話我唔關心佢我都好委屈㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5593d5df2a187d52cdaded5c27701219fb6cff34","tid":1687030,"uid":252151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"dont treat her like a normal person.<br />\nunderstand the symptoms first, then can explain more abt her unreasonable behaviour.<br />\navoid expressing emotions too much, e.g. annoyed/worried/too concerned.<br />\ngive space and time to her<br />\n<br />\ndepends on the current episode, <br />\nbut medication management, increase daytime engagement and physical exercises are important anyways.<br />\nfind ways that can calm her down, e.g. music/sleep/rest/relaxation exercises. time-out when she is out of control, avoid direct conflicts, give empathy when necessary<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔係好識 上堂係咁教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88879aef951fe36d7b510e023b65eb123d00f68c","tid":1687030,"uid":293803,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"我媽媽都係，甚至到自己都有抑鬱。<br />\n用盡一切方法，但都忍唔到，最後選擇左離家出走。<br />\n我好明白果種覺得自己不孝既感覺😭不停同自己講明明我都好痛苦，點解一定要我就你，佢果種情緒勒索實在太難受。點解我係女兒無得到母愛之餘仲要照顧返你。同時覺得自己咁對媽媽好衰。"},{"pid":"7b36ae32e1baf2cd685fd8a78828681f9ea11ebe","tid":1687030,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ae517c4e10eff4bb0c51e1f2bbadb232fc87bd0","tid":1687030,"uid":311164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7489dd9bd49a23b120c402d39a8a11dcf5e11a95","tid":1687030,"uid":321803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"帶佢睇醫生，有藥物可幫助穩定情緒<br />\n另外樓主都要比多啲愛心包容你媽咪，<br />\n你媽咪唔係想搞事，可能係個病令佢控制唔到情緒，<br />\n先至有啲唔好既說話/行為<br />\n<br />\n你識得上網搵幫手已經好叻👍🏻 <br />\n希望你媽咪可以搵到個好醫生"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"佢係我出世前已經有病同睇開醫生，係呢幾年愈演愈烈，都頂咗好耐，嗰點係佢郁啲就話我唔關心佢我都好委屈㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:22:33.000Z"